## Level 3

### Description  
> The password for Century4 is the number of files on the desktop.



Typical pipeline utilizing version:
```powershell
Get-ChildItem -File | Measure-Object | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Count
```

Short, console style version:
```powershell
(ls).Count
```

